### Create New Patient (through the gateway -> requires the JWT from login.http)
### This EVICTS "patientsList" and CACHE-PUTs the new patient into "patients",
### so the next GET /api/patients is a fresh DB read again.
POST http://localhost:4004/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "address": "123 Main Street",
  "dateOfBirth": "1985-06-15",
  "email": "test-redis-testing--@example.com",
  "name": "John Deo Redis",
  "registeredDate": "2024-11-28"
}

> {% client.global.set("patientId", response.body.id) %}

###